Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？ 小满也看电视了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,海豚搁浅那么多还能全部得救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微对自己魔法使的身份感到自豪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小空在东京很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了 我交上新朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是个魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不错嘛 该不会连男朋友都有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 小满你真讨厌
Comment: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真的很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 总觉得很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我决定去见一下远山君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是多亏了小空 多亏了那场雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我在海边说了那么狂妄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你不要抢在前面道歉好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是多亏了小空才能使用魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次涌现那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然也不算是谢礼 我想带你去看个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想带我去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是海吧 叫「江之岛」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想带我去的地方就是那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,光我们两个人一起 感觉像是在约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这「像」是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有家店的套餐不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要稍微走几步路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我冲浪后经常去的店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,豪太 自从第一天被纱织老师骂了就再也没去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那天在回去的电车上 我就下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时不去冲浪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 大概是想有了后路就会逃避魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,才没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只是觉得这段时间还是不要去冲浪了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢 第一次遇到豪太的时候 搞错了下车的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,走了很长的路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那时你的魔法太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可你却数落人家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那时发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈离开了家 有点失落
Comment: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这墨鱼蘸酱油吃味道很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大海在闪闪发亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 绿川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是山吹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在看海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是山吹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跟谁在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 和铃木
Comment: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,天公作美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,风和日丽真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你想 今天是最后一天休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要不要和大家出去玩一玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我真没想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,山吹很细心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,今天实在是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 替我向小空问好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,自己房里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,声音听起来很消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,难得这么好天气的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,难得有天气这么好的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要来吃大份冰激凌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,中野有一家很大的雪糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来追我 来追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真想让妈妈也来看一看这片海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下次把她带上不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 看到你爸爸了吗
Comment: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你妈妈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,到海之家放寻人启事吧
Comment: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你叫什么名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你叫什么名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不能把名字告诉陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,骑脖子就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,骑脖子没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,草太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,草太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 是我家小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 都说了不能自己跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很活泼的小朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真是麻烦你们了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你呀 担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,草太 是空（Sora）的So和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,豪太（Ta）的Ta
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,草太真的很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的啦 开玩笑的
Comment: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,空 等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,空 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是生沙丁鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,超好吃
Comment: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,跟过节一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉像过节一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,电扶梯是什么？
Comment: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可以走石阶 也可以坐电扶梯去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可以走石阶上去 也可以坐电扶梯上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很科技的感觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,反重力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是…反重力？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是第一次坐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 是神签
Comment: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,豪太的怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,豪太的签怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是超普通的中吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Comment: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看看嘛 喂
Comment: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,豪太说要我看的地方就是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,豪太说要带我去看的地方就是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还要再走一段路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好多坡道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还很远？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 请随便坐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次来这里的时候我也吃了一惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里真的很壮观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 跟爸爸一起来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 这样根本喝不了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有吸管吗 用那个喝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 来碟酱菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小朋友真的很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下次什么时候有休假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,后天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那大后天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是工作
Comment: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那再下一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那再后一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可能放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就陪我一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,菜要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 江之岛盖饭里面是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天在海里捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大海里的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是纪念品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.59,up_default,,0,0,0,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:08.89,up_default,,0,0,0,,是 是 不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.43,up_default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.10,up_default,,0,0,0,,呐呐 给我骑骑脖子
Comment: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.56,up_default,,0,0,0,,不要啦…我都醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.56,up_default,,0,0,0,,诶 不要啊…我都醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.89,up_default,,0,0,0,,有什么不好嘛
Comment: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这不也挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,青春吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 是江之岛买来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,从山吹日向那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,俩人一起去海边了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好想大伙儿一起去啊 海边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛叫我笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你一说话就得端着架子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,铃木空和绿川豪太两个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么黑田浩二你要脸红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早 今天也好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,海边…玩得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小空玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想去一次海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是豪太君邀请的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,绿川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法完全不行的你居然爆发出那种力量 超感动咧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,阿部和水口都很感动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好感动哦 绿川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 绿川同学太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是迷上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,绿川 握个手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟我握手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明天的课从9点开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大家小心不要中暑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很受欢迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是戏弄我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在绿川也成为了不起的魔法使了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你挺拽嘛 跟浅葱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,浅葱指浅的葱吗…
Comment: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢冷笑话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢冷笑话吗…
Comment: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 全身都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这雷听起来很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 刚好天晴了 唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是翻唱MOONRIDERS的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pistol Pinok 奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你招牌灯亮着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是还在营业
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那来杯酒吧 要烈一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,高中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,社会青年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 你也真够邋遢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,钱我有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不巧 我们这没有卖给自暴自弃小孩的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别放这么闷的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我已经没有归处了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要咖喱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我不喜欢撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:23:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但也有不能把真相说出来的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,豪太 我还是说不出口啊 对不起…
